  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Total Hip Arthroplasty is equal to or better than Hemiarthroplasty in the treatment of
      displaced femoral neck fractures in the elderly-elderly
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Total Hip Arthroplasty is equal to or better alternative to Hemiarthroplasty in the treatment
      of displaced femoral neck fractures in the elderly-elderly (patients 80 years and over).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
